Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:13.23,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,An asteroid named VR-1 is approaching Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:16.07,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It is approximately two \Nkilometers in diameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:19.86,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The asteroid that supposedly \Ndrove dinosaurs to extinction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.94,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,is estimated at about ten \Nkilometers in diameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:26.61,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,You can easily imagine the \Ndamage that will be caused
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:28.71,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,if VR-1 hits Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:32.50,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been widely reported by \Norganizations internationally
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:36.83,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,that the possibility of a direct \Nimpact is highly impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:38.72,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,but those are all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.46,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,A collision is imminent,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:47.84,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and it will happen on the\N31st of December at 11:55 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.72,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the U.S. government \Nand the other leading nations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.89,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,have conspired to hide the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.02,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.86,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they have formed a secret \Nagreement between themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:02.23,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,These so-called leaders have been evacuating
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:05.98,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,into nuclear shelters that have \Nbeen kept secret from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:12.58,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,They fear riots will occur if the \Nexistence of the shelters is made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:15.96,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan to save only themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:19.08,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving the rest of the world to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:21.93,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not allow for such conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:26.51,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,We want the U.S. and Japanese government\Nto disclose the truth, immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.94,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the demand from us, the {\i0}Qmay Group{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:32.17,Punchline-Qmay-kai,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Showdown! \NWhat is the \NQmay Group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.70,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense. VR-1 colliding with Earth? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.56,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's their doomsday philosophies \Nthat are the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.88,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Qmay Group members believe \Nin the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.31,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, they may be trying to \Nmake it happen themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.18,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to carry out the vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:51.96,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,of their recently-deceased \Nleader, Tsubouchi Qmei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:54.71,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:59.22,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The Qmay Group says the \Nasteroid is going to hit, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:05.02,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So the governments and specialists are lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:09.01,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it the Qmay Group \Nthat wants to end humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:13.61,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he said their leader Tsubouchi Qmei died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.69,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the person \Npossessing my body is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.20,Punchline-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you open the door for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.85,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.54,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.17,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yakushimaru Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:18.08,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, a Christmas tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.44,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you make {\i1}that{\i0} mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.80,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Right here should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.09,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.53,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:29.06,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking we should have a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.29,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.91,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want to do it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.80,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.25,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:42.19,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Jingle bells, jingle bells, \Nhere come the Martians!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.13,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.70,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,All right, switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.81,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No, Muhi, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:55.74,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's something I've been wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:56.85,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.48,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,It's about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.81,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura! Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.52,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.96,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.62,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have believed it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.73,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Is Strange Juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:19.56,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Meika-emon, I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.24,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.82,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,The Martians!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.68,Punchline-Ep_Title2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,#03
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.68,Punchline-Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Martians Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.43,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Ito, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.68,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? She's not even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:39.06,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I brought all this stuff because \Nshe wanted to have a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.46,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.94,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you're Ito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.31,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.24,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where's Mikatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.08,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.05,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, I wonder where she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.08,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there something you \Nwanted to ask me, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.32,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's about you and Mikatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.42,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.23,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Narugino-kun and I go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.43,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well say we're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.26,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Then you knew Rabura because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.93,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I've known about her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.59,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,She showed me pictures on her phone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.19,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a blatant lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.69,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,But that still doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:27.19,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.35,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.67,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:33.20,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, before that, do you mind \Nif I use your bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.48,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you going to close the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.79,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I like to live on the wild side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.70,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be that way even \Nwhen I'm in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.44,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.97,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave ho, heave ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.73,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,No way! How could I be a Martian?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:05.73,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle uniform with super\N high-tech camouflage technology!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.75,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Tou-maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.20,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to use this to try to confuse Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.16,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.71,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just have to be \Ncareful not to make noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:34.67,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:38.14,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... I rolled off the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.21,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What? How...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.90,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.65,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a secret passage \Nor something in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.65,Punchline-Top,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.42,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:49.50,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Let me look inside, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.02,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Strange Juice is doing her business in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.41,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? She has the door wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.52,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.79,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.25,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Strange Juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.81,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,True, I may have my wild side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:10.20,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't let my wildness \Nout into the wild right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.30,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.61,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I guess I'll go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.23,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.61,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some time before the party starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.31,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.93,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.07,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Snore, snore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.03,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.57,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.47,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.97,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,You get it now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.87,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Narugino-kun and I are two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.84,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,We're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.10,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:46.88,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.88,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's something\NI want your advice about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.00,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,My advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.11,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:58.93,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.52,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.52,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.19,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:14.78,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.11,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.37,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Hand him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.37,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.50,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Tou-maker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.38,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.25,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.64,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.95,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.75,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... It won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.67,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:19.39,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.06,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:21.99,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:22.89,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.02,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, he won't die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.77,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Just hand him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.81,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That emblem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.90,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.07,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.47,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Your spirit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.33,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Use your spirit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.33,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Look what Rabura just threw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:53.75,Punchline-Flashback,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Cinnamon has a strange effect \Nthat increases your spirit power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.87,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.51,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.26,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.65,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.05,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.33,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.49,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.58,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,There's no cinnamon here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.50,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What do I do, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.25,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.23,Punchline-To_Rain,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose not to rain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.00,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Losing neither to rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.68,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,nor to the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.75,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,That is the sort of person I want to become!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:52.01,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Super helper-man of justice, \NMiyazawa Kenji, is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.69,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.47,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.22,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Miyazawa Kenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.78,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.31,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.87,Punchline-Top,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hang on! Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.87,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He's totally weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.88,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm off my game today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.81,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Must be this crick in my neck from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.11,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Enough nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.80,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just give me twenty seconds, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.28,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,What if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.76,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Do I get a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.11,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.20,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.19,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:26.89,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.47,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give me that promised reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.03,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.23,Default,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:42.24,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,This is your reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.29,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.41,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.38,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.33,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.60,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.31,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.35,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,His wound's healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.82,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.78,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Strange Ju—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.53,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:43.15,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Meika-emon, I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:56.60,Punchline-News_Low_Headline,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Bus hijacking\Nmastermind on the run
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.43,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect, Teraoka, is thought
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.33,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,to be the mastermind behind the \NQmay Group hostage incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.76,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The police believe he is still on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:05.07,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, why have I lost days again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:09.41,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to go to that party yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.87,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.46,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The party was yesterday, not on the Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.48,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,On December 25th, Christmas Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.87,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,After that incident with the intruder and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.87,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.18,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Who was he, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:26.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,He had a Qmay Group emblem on his bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.85,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi's wound looked like it healed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:33.10,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And that freak Miyazawa \NKenji guy is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.60,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And above all, Meika...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.52,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:42.85,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.27,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just returning a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.20,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You need to do repairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:51.01,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Your fusion reactor broke \Ndown after that man hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.28,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.33,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.27,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyazawa Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.64,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a sick child to the east,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.26,Punchline-Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,it is my duty to go and care for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:06.21,Punchline-Flashback,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're not a child, but a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.90,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.97,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's a view of your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.26,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Meika dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.51,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's trying to help with Japan's \Ndeclining birth rate and rising age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.82,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, she's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.61,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.96,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she in her underwear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.20,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.12,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.16,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.08,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I just forgot to \Nput on my insulation ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.59,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I need it in order to install replacement parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.25,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this rubber thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.75,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't fixed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:51.47,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an aftereffect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.51,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,My radiator broke after that guy hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.55,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.02,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.02,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito and Muhi are both gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.52,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \NIto was acting weird yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.10,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.16,Punchline-Level_Up,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Necromancer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.16,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit power level went up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.05,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.94,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.47,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,That's such an unimaginative name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.71,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.01,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.11,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika's playing Strange Juice's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? We talked \Nabout it at last night's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.48,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.39,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Code Name Pumpkin Chair, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.26,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know \Nwhat they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.50,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mikatan next door, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.61,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, but she's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.15,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear her clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.76,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why've you been so grumpy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.86,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because {\i1}it{\i0} hasn't arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.64,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.66,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the thing that comes once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.41,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.15,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika's you-know-what hasn't arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.50,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,The once-a-month thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.76,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.54,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.28,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Handstand Beginners Monthly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.73,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You have a subscription, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.61,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.14,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.80,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't do handstands yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.31,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.12,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,See? Positive result.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:23.83,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,She really is expecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.77,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.09,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.70,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,How much did you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.38,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,About three months, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.94,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Three months?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.48,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that when you have \Nto get the most rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.60,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick. I think I'm gonna puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.91,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.58,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Morning sickness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.89,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.75,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot to put this on again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.38,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, why don't you learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.30,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you \Nput it in without the rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.96,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Without the rubber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.47,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,P-Put it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.16,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.21,Punchline-Names,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Io Ruka (17)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:08.55,Punchline-Names,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hikiotani Ito (17)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:10.54,Punchline-This_Year,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,333)}Those are this year's victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.01,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,This year's victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.53,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura-san's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.88,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.92,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Meika-emon, don't you have \Nsomething to bring her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.68,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.80,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Daihatsu Tenga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.76,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.97,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He's a world-renowned genius inventor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.64,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,But eight years ago, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.50,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.99,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,He left me and this Korai House behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:50.93,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,And Meika inherited the professor's fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.90,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.49,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,My census registrations?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.59,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:00.53,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,She hacked into the public \Noffice and rewrote the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.11,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.64,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Meika has godly hacking skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.94,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,If she wanted to, she could even \Nlaunch every nuke in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.92,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:15.22,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Then Professor Tenga \Nmade all these machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:19.55,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No, Grandpa's inventions \Nare mostly kept in storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.05,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:25.05,Punchline-Reizoukou,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Reizoukou
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.06,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,One is the Reizoukou in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.49,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The other is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.44,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I was born here in Korai House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:35.02,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Here, twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.05,Punchline-Reizoukou,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,450)}Twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.33,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Korai House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:50.93,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Over the next few years, Grandpa \Ntaught me all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:56.86,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Academic knowledge,\Ncooking, all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:02.34,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how much he taught me, \Nthere was one thing I couldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:10.55,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandpa, why can't I do handstands?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:12.85,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not just handstands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:16.11,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at anything athletic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:21.61,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Meika, don't think that just because \Nyou're a robot, you can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:26.37,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Robots all have their own roles and duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:31.08,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,A robot is made to be adept at their duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.31,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's my duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:37.88,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,A few years from now, \Nyou'll meet a certain girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:43.63,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,A member of Justice Punch, the secret \Nforce that will one day save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.80,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.76,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:52.31,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,Your duty is to protect her, \Nraise her, and assist her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:56.77,Punchline-Flashback,Tenga,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, maybe I should say it's Heaven's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.82,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:10.32,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew Korai House held such a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.56,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-tan, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:23.63,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.95,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm not gonna—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.05,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
